Format:
python vis.py <topology file> <log file> <node color refresh True/False> <cycle interval>

Topology File:
refer to topo.txt and topo2.txt

Log File:
refer to log.txt

Log File format
<time>:SENT:<src>:<dest>:<topic>:<message>:<lamport timestamp>      AT the time putting out going q
<time>:RECV:<dest>:<topic>:<message>:<is_subscriber>:<lamport timestamp> after subscription check
<time>:ARIV:<src>:<dest>   Sender deposits to incoming q
<time>:ANODE:<node>:<cnodeA, cnodeB,...>:<costA, costB,...>  Add node - event
<time>:RNODE:<node>   remove node event



